    },
    "body": "- Replace `java-release.yml` workflow with `gpr-publish.yml` to support automated publishing to GitHub Packages and release artifact uploads.\r\n- Add `GitHubPrivateArtifacts` repository to `settings.gradle.kts` with credential support.\r\n- Replace local JAR file dependencies in `plugin` module with remote artifacts: `bluebird-extnfc:1.0.0` and `sam-ng:1.0.0`.\r\n- Update `plugin-mock` artifact ID to `${rootProject.name}-mock` in Maven publication.\r\n- Configure `GitHubPackages` publishing repository in `plugin` and `plugin-mock` modules.\r\n- Lower `androidMinSdk` from 28 to 26 in `gradle.properties`.\r\n- Wrap debug log statements with `logger.isDebugEnabled` checks in `BluebirdCardReaderAdapter.kt` to optimize performance.",
